Package rocks.xmpp.extensions.filetransfer.model

Interface FileTransferOffer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileTransferOfferEvent, JingleFileTransfer.File, SIFileTransferOffer
    public interface FileTransferOffer
    An interface for file transfer requests, which covers XEP-0066, XEP-0096 and XEP-0234.
    See Also:
    XEP-0066: Out of Band Data, XEP-0096: SI File Transfer, XEP-0234: Jingle File Transfer

    • Method Summary
